<h2>What is Lowsars? 什么是Lowsars?</h2>
<p>Lowsars is short for "Lightweight OI Wonderful Scoring and Ranking System". It is a free (GPL) software used for testing Olympiad in Informatics(OI) programs, and give the scores and rankings.</p>
<p>Lowsars is written in bash and xslt, and mainly works on GNU/Linux.</p>
<p>Lowsars是“轻量级OI奇妙的评测系统”的简称。它是用来测试信息学奥林匹克竞赛(OI)程序，并能够给出成绩和排名的GPL自由软件。</p>
<p>Lowsars 由 bash 和 xslt 写成，主要在GNU/Linux系统上运行。</p>
